snippet.title: Dragon Age, Journeys - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Another free Web/Flash RPG I tried out recently.

Found it a little sluggish at first but once you get used to it you realize it's quite a polished little system and looks good, too - Will definately watch out for the next part (Sadly it's kinda short, but should burn a few hours of your time).
